quran[4]{c,v,t}:
  2,142,"∆Āen njofi…óu…ďe faa…óa hakkil en ka alyahuuda, e nanndo ma…ď…ďe ka naafiqii…ďe …ďen wi'oyay: E ko hoccintini juul…ďe …ďen ga'e Qibla suudu almaqdisi ndun ndu …ďe fewtaynoo?! Jaabor-…ďe -An nulaa…óo- :Ko Allah gooto On heeranii laamu fu…ónaange e hiirnaange e baŇčŇčeejo goo ko wanaa …óin,Himo fewtinira on mo O muuyi e jiyaa…ďe Makko nokku kala ka O yi…ói, KaŇčko On Senii…óo,Himo fewnira on O muuyi e jiyaa…ďe Makko …ďen faade e laawol feewungol;ngol oo√Īaaki ngol …ďoylaaki."
  2,143,"Ko wano Men wa…óirani on non Qibla mo Men su…ďanii on; Men wa…óiri on mofte su…ďaa…óe nun…óu…óe,hakindii…óe ndeer mofte …óen fof, ka fi…ďndeeji,ka dewe e ka gollodal; no laatoroyon √Īalnde darngal seeditaŇčtoo…ďe Nulaa…óo Allah on kon ko Alla yamirnoo on yottinnde e mofte mo'on,e no Nulaa…óo Muhammadu (yo O his) laatoroya seeditoytoo…óo e mo'on wo'nde O yottinii kon ko O nulanoo e mo'on.Men wa…óiraali kadi waylugol Qibla on mo fewtayno-…óaa e mu'un;e maanaa bayt al maqdisi on, si wanaa no men anndira -anndal fee√Īugol yowondiragl e njo…ďdi- on ja…ďay…óo (yarlora) shari'a Allah On,o jebbilora mo,o jokka Nulaa…óo on, e [no men anndira] on muurtoowo e diine mu'un,o jokka mbelee…óe makko, hara o jebbilortaa konko Allah Shar'inani.Gom…óii waylugol Qibla on ka arannde, laatino huunde mawnde si wanaa e dow …ďen …ďen Allah hawrinndini e gom…óinnde …óum,e wo'nde kala ko O Shar'inani jiyaa…ďe Makko …ďen ko √Īee√Īal yottiingal.Allah Laatoraali yeeboowo liimanaaku mo'on, ko e Makko juulde mon nden ado wayleede Qibla hewtata, pellet, Allah ko Hilnotoo…óo yim…ďe …ďen Yurmee …ďe,O Sa…ótinaŇčtaa…ďe,O yeebataa sawaaba golleeji ma…ď…ďe."
  2,144,"Gom…óii Men yi'ii - ko an yo Annabiijo- wayloragol yeeso maa ngon e ndaar…óe maa …óen ka baŇčŇče kammu, sabbitagol ette-ettennoo fii jipporagol wahyu on waylireede Qibla on ka yi…óu-…óaa, ma Men Fewtinire e Qibla mo yi…óu-…óaa welani maa - ko on woni suudu Allah hormorteendu ndun- o lomtoo baytul maqdisi on, fewtinir yeeso maa ngon baŇčŇče suudu Allah hormorteendu ndun, kala ka ngon…óon - onon gom…óim…ďe- fewtiree e baŇčŇče mayru tuma juulo-ton. Pellet, …ďen Rokkaa…ďe Deftere …ďen immorde e yahuuda e Nasaara en, hi…ďe anndi wo'nde wayleede Qibla on ko goonga jippor…óo ka Tag…óo-…ďe On Kippu-…óo fiyakuuji ma…ď…ďe; tawde …óum no tabiti ka deftere ma…ď…ďe, Allah non Welsindoraali kon ko …ďen …óuurnii…ďe e goonga gollata, ko woni, KaŇčko Senii…óo On Himo anndi …óum, ma O yo…ďiroy…ďe …óum."
  2,145,"Mi woondii si an -annabiijo on- a addidanii …ďen rokkaa…ďe deftere nden immorde e alyahuuda e annasaare en,wondude e kala maande e burhaanu,wo'nde wayleede Qibla on ko goonga,a wonaali kadi fewtiroowo e qibla ma…ď…ďe …ďaawa nde Allah yiltu-maa e …óum,yoga e ma…ď…ďe kadi fewtirtaa e qibla yoga;sabu fedde kala e ma…ď…ďe hino heefer…óina ndeya. Pellet si a jokkii mbelee…óe …ďee …óoo ko faati e Qibla on e ko wanaa …óum immorde e shari'aaji e √Īaawooje …ďaawo nde anndal sellungal ngal sikke alaa e mu'un ari e maa;an dey ontuma a jeyaama e too√Īir…ďe selugol peewal ngal, jokka mbelee…óe.Ko Annabiijo on(Yo O his)yeewtaa …óoo kon,ko tinndingol kaanude jokkugol …ďe,sabu Allah da…óndii Annabiijo Makko on e …óum,ko jeertinnde mofte makko …óen si o fe∆ī∆īii."